> Thanks @maziyarpanahi Have you tested it against the lower version of spark such as spark 2.3 ?

@zjffdu Very good question! I am going to build this pull request with `-Pspark 2.3` and `-Pspark 2.4` and see how Spark 2.3.x works in both just to be sure from the builds and working with Spark as well.

I'll do it now and let you know ASAP!

**Complete custom single-menu & multi-menu test.**

Custom single-menu test code:
```
    Map<String, String> infos = new java.util.HashMap<String, String>();
    infos.put("jobUrl", "jobUrl");
    infos.put("label", "SPARK JOB");
    infos.put("tooltip", "View in Spark web UI");
    infos.put("noteId", context.getNoteId());
    infos.put("paraId", context.getParagraphId());
    context.getIntpEventClient().onParaInfosReceived(infos);
```
